  "title": "Production Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities :-</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the smooth operation of all aircon duct work activities.</li>\n  <li>Perform maintenance of all tools, equipment, machines and facilities.</li>\n  <li>Perform form factor conversion of machines and carry out routine preventive      maintenance.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a healthy spare parts inventory.</li>\n  <li>Minimize production material wastage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min 2 years working experience in factory production.</li>\n  <li>Able to handle english and Mandarin speaking associates</li>\n  <li>Independent, matured, good communicator, hardworking and disciplined.</li>\n</ul>",
